<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 jīn xiāo gē zuì tián, jīn xiāo gē zuì liàng,
 jīn xiāo wǒ men dà tuán yuán. xīn zhōng xǐ yáng yáng.
 wèn hán yòu wèn nuǎn. xiāng jù zài tīng táng.
 zhù fú jiā zhōng měi wèi qīn rén shēn tǐ dōu ān kāng.
 dú jīng yǒu liàng guāng, dǎo gào yǒu fāng xiàng.
 dài lǐng qún yáng yǒu yì xiàng, bù lí zhǔ shēn páng.
 wǒ men tóng gān kǔ, wǒ men tóng gē chàng.
 shén de dào yuè fā guǎng chuán, yuè lái yuè xìng wàng.</lyrics>
<title>jīn xiāo gē zuì tián 迦南1174</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
